<header id="intro" class="t__section intro">
    <div class="t__container">
        <figure class="intro__avatar">
            {% include 'components/avatar.njk' %}
            <div class="intro__avatar__ascii">
                {% include 'assets/ascii.svg' %}
            </div>
        </figure>
        <h1 class="intro__logo">
            <span class="t__vh">{{ site.author }}</span>
            {% include 'assets/logo.svg' %}
        </h1>
        <p class="t__lead">Hello! I'm {{ site.author }}, a seasoned designer with a journey spanning {% experience %}+ years. Originally from Ukraine, I've now set my creative compass to Dublin, Ireland. I advocate for accessibility, aesthetics and functionality, finding immense potential in simplicity. In my product design career, I've had the privilege of collaborating with esteemed clients such as:</p>
        {% if clients %}
            <ol class="intro__clients t__inline">
                {% for client in clients %}
                    <li class="intro__clients__item t__inline__item t__inline__item--1">
                        {% include 'clients/' + client.title | slug + '.svg' %}
                    </li>
                {% endfor %}
            </ol>
        {% endif %}
    </div>
</header>
